Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:11.48,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Alright, my next class is in another room.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:15.65,Megumi,,0,0,0,,At least music class can be pretty enjoyable–\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:20.01,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Megumi. Perfect timing.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:21.44,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Hm?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:27.38,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind staying behind in the clubroom after practice this afternoon?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:29.75,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay…?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:32.63,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Alright, I’ll see you later, then.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.32,Megumi,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:42.41,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…Huh? What did I do?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:51.03,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,The wind is gentle today, so the clouds are relaxed.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:55.65,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’m sure the night stars will be happy, too.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:56.77,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Night…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:00:58.77,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Hmmm…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:00.89,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Dark…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:03.46,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Dark, dark…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:05.79,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Light switch…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:08.39,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Mmm…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:09.81,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Futon…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.11,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’m getting kinda sleepy.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:19.01,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri, could I have a moment?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:22.32,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Sure. Do you feel sleepy too, Kozu?\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:26.13,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to you after our club meeting.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.68,0:01:27.32,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Huh…?\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:31.32,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That’s all. I’ll see you then.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:38.23,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Did I do something wrong again…?\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:40.52,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Ah… the wind…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.40,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,It’s gotten a little colder…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:46.23,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I think…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:53.61,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for staying behind, you two.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:59.50,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…But why are both of you sitting so far away?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.34,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Well…\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:06.00,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,We don’t know what you’re scolding us for…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:07.80,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Scolding?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:11.34,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Am I supposed to be scolding you?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:13.42,Kozue,,0,0,0,,For what?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:18.33,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Well, with the way you asked us, what else were we supposed to think!?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:19.96,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Huh…?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:23.32,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I thought I invited you here pretty normally…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:27.80,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Nope! It was exactly how the guidance counselor would do it!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:29.69,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Definitely.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:35.67,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Do you two get really called to the guidance office that often…?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.36,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Never mind.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:45.79,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I asked you two to stay today because I wanted to discuss something less than pleasant…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.90,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,We really are getting scolded…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.12,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I have two sheets of paper here with me.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:57.20,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…Are those withdrawal forms for me and Tsuzuri…!?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:03:02.06,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…Ah! You’re planning on weeding out misbehaving club members!? Is that it!?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:06.11,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Deepest apologies. I will listen intently in class starting tomorrow.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:12.18,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Should I forget my textbooks, I will go back to the dorm to get it instead of just waving it off with an “Oh well.”\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:15.49,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Those are all things you should already be doing, though…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:20.42,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But nevertheless, it seems there’s been a misunderstanding.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.10,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What I wanted to talk about today was…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:27.04,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,The promise the three of us made…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:36.20,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…To go our separate ways and not interfere with each other after we withdrew from nationals.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:41.05,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This is what the three of us decided after advancing beyond the Hokuriku qualifier.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:47.10,Kozue,,0,0,0,,The paper that Megumi wrote, and that we all signed our names on.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:53.98,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Last year I truly believed that this was the best path forward.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:58.29,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Megumi was injured, and we lost Sachi-senpai.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:06.93,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And in my desire to protect the club and advance past the sectional qualifier, I hurt Tsuzuri.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:11.48,Kozue,,0,0,0,,We argued countless times in what we could only call clashes of ideas,\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.21,Kozue,,0,0,0,,yet in reality, we were only pitting our egos against each other.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:19.17,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This is the proof of our prior naïveté…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:23.85,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Our sapling certification, if you will.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:29.05,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I wanted to once again have an earnest discussion about this.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:37.45,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If there is anything you two have not yet told me, I want to hear it so I can come to terms with it.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:44.12,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If I could have done things a little differently, a little better, then maybe…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:48.83,Megumi,,0,0,0,,What, you would have stopped me from getting injured?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:53.07,Megumi,,0,0,0,,You would’ve stopped me from separating myself from the group for a year?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.23,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.59,Megumi,,0,0,0,,You’re so arrogant, Kozue.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.05,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Megu…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:03.72,Megumi,,0,0,0,,The only cause of my injury was my injury.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:06.78,Megumi,,0,0,0,,The only reason I couldn’t dance was because I couldn’t dance.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:10.28,Megumi,,0,0,0,,That’s it. There’s no hidden meaning behind those things.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:15.05,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And despite all that, the two of you still helped with my rehab.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:18.61,Megumi,,0,0,0,,You cut into your practice time, and even your own personal time for me.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:23.04,Megumi,,0,0,0,,That’s why I stopped being a school idol.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:26.09,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I decided that myself.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.43,Megumi,,0,0,0,,You don’t see it?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:30.01,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Right there, on the text we signed our names on.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:34.12,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Maybe you’re the club president now,\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:42.83,Megumi,,0,0,0,,but to us, both the Kozue then and the Kozue now are just a classmate who’s a little more dependable than our other ones.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:49.01,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And yet you still try to harbor our burdens, every single time.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:50.76,Megumi,,0,0,0,,It’s so irritating.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:52.86,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Megumi…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:57.60,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I don’t think I have as much say on this as Megu.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:04.20,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,It was my fault you forced yourself to do all those things.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:10.10,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,When I think about what happened last year, it feels like my body’s sinking.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:16.23,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Like I’m going deeper into a dark ocean, and the light’s getting further away.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:22.95,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,If this is what regrets are like, then I’ve always regretted it.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:28.57,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,If only I talked to Kozu more…\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.10,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Megu too.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.21,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:38.98,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,And maybe I could even take the role of president.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:41.55,Megumi,,0,0,0,,No, I think that’s a bit much…!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.23,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…You two.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:49.24,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Alright, enough with all this downer talk!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:52.93,Megumi,,0,0,0,,The three of us were missing useful life experience, so things weren’t ideal!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.24,Megumi,,0,0,0,,That’s it! Any problems with that!?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:56.95,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.41,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I said, no more!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:05.19,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Do you plan on spending the rest of our lives apologizing for what happened last year!?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:09.70,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m happy the way things are now, so there’s no use reopening old wounds!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:14.72,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I think you should learn how to take things more lightly, Kozu.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.51,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Like a cloud.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:21.19,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Whether it’s your relationships with other people, or your studies, or your school idol work,\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:24.41,Megumi,,0,0,0,,you always treat everything the same.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:29.27,Megumi,,0,0,0,,If there’s something you can’t do, you keep at it until you can.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:33.71,Megumi,,0,0,0,,You think you can’t do things because you’re not working hard enough.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:35.82,Kozue,,0,0,0,,T-That’s…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.49,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Well, isn’t that the way it is?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:43.29,Megumi,,0,0,0,,If I were you, I’d give up after an hour.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.36,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’d give myself five seconds.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.62,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.81,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It upsets me, too.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.77,Kozue,,0,0,0,,When I’m not up to things,\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:57.83,Kozue,,0,0,0,,it always ends with someone sad.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:03.09,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If I could, I’d like to be as perfect as music is.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:11.90,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Like a piece of sheet music, if even one aspect is missing, then it ceases to be perfect.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.73,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri, grab onto Kozue’s cheeks and pull!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.83,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Nyoooom.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.43,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Scyoosh me!?\N(Excuse me!?)\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.78,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Now you’re no longer perfect!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.14,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Far from ideal, eh!?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:27.29,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Come on! I was trying to have a serious conversation!\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:30.73,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Good grief…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.59,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…But thank you.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:42.87,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Everything feels a little lighter now.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.25,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Only a little?\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.93,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Progress is progress.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:50.15,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Kozue likes carrying everything on her shoulders, after all.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:55.59,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I don’t… think that’s true.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:01.19,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,So, what about this… sapling certification, you called it?\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:02.72,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,What do we do with it?\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.60,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Hmmm, rip it up into a million tiny pieces and throw them away?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:12.55,Megumi,,0,0,0,,If we don’t do anything with it, Kozue will probably frame it on her wall as a “warning” or something.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:20.51,Kozue,,0,0,0,,B-But, reflecting on one’s mistakes is important for personal growth…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.41,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Wait, you seriously were gonna do it!?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:27.56,Megumi,,0,0,0,,If you keep punishing yourself like that, you’ll sound like someone with one of {\i1}those{\i0} hobbies!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.34,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s not like I really was going to!\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:34.45,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Anyway, let’s just take it home for now.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:43.24,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Having nothing around the school makes the stars look really pretty, huh?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:46.98,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I appreciate this path back to the dorms.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.19,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You can see a variety of different stars in each season.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:56.15,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Huh? Didn’t you say you had two papers earlier?\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:58.15,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,What was the other one?\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:01.09,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I wasn’t just imagining it, was I?\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.51,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I didn’t forget about it.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:07.01,Kozue,,0,0,0,,There just wasn’t a good time to show it to you.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:10.91,Megumi,,0,0,0,,An entry form for Love Live!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:13.03,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,It’s just like last year’s.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.73,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, things are different this year.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:20.78,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Last year, only Tsuzuri and I were registered to perform.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:23.55,Megumi,,0,0,0,,This year, we’ve got six people! Three subunits!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.86,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,DOLLCHESTRA can perform.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:27.36,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That’s right.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:31.41,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This year we can do what we really wanted to do.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:39.24,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Well, naturally, that isn’t to say that I didn’t learn anything from performing with Tsuzuri last year…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:41.17,Kozue,,0,0,0,,but I digress.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:44.98,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,The way you said that reminds me of Saya.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:49.30,Megumi,,0,0,0,,The day Mira-Cra Park! can change the world is finally here!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:54.96,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Cerise Bouquet can surely rise the ranks and become the strongest of school idols.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.84,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Just as I dreamed that day.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.95,Megumi,,0,0,0,,But no matter who wins or loses, no grudges, okay?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:04.95,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:08.48,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,But Saya and I are the best.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:13.58,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is our genius here calling her shot already~!?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:19.43,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I can’t tell if you two are each other’s best friends or worst enemies.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:25.45,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…But the three of us have a truly irreplaceable bond.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:33.06,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If a single one of us were missing, we wouldn’t be the “Hasu Big Three,” after all.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:35.68,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Hasu Big Three.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.21,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri…?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.29,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I had a great idea.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:41.21,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Let’s fold a star.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.13,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Let’s do our best today as well!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:05.42,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Low population density means a happy Ruri!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.49,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Good morning.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:09.49,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I look forward to today’s club session.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:14.07,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh? What’s this origami star?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:16.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Oh, you’re right…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:18.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,This wasn’t here yesterday, right?\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:21.22,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,That used to be a sapling.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:25.09,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,But now, it’s a beautiful star.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:28.22,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan, translation {\i1}please{\i0}!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:32.24,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh!? Sorry, I don’t know, either!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:36.54,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,And its name is the Hasu Big Three.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.54,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.97,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But there’s only one star!?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.14,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…I mean, it sounds nice, but…\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.23,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I think it’s a great idea.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:52.71,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Rather than destroying our past, we’ve turned it into a star.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:55.13,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…Heh, maybe.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:56.57,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I think so.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:00.30,Kozue,,0,0,0,,In any case… Everyone!\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.38,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Let’s give today’s practice our best!\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.26,NPC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Okaaay!\N{\fs35}[Kaho & Sayaka & Tsuzuri & Rurino & Megumi]
